{"tid":1704233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"搞清楚 1111黎明行動=各區早上開花 同三罷係有本質上嘅分別","createTime":"2019-11-10T15:17:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T15:23:07.000Z","uid":77393,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"df32b0414e016de8fec051da85827af4beff25eb","tid":1704233,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"見有人不斷指出三罷係需要時間醞釀 各行各業嘅工會係需要時間建立 呢個說法係好正確<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但<br />\n1111黎明行動<br />\n並不等於三罷<br />\n<br />\n而係各區早上開花<br />\n令到所有港豬被罷工<br />\n令到學生被罷課<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁由邊個負責開花<br />\n係所有抗爭者呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n各位返工嘅手足唔好諗住朝早起身就等睇新聞好似等運到咁<br />\n<br />\n只要大家主動去開花 你就可以為自己製造藉口罷工<br />\n<br />\n唔好諗住坐享其成<br />\n唔好再將抗爭責任推去學生身上<br />\n<br />\n已經有義士犧牲 唔好再等到其他犧牲者出現先換嚟兩三日嘅團結<br />\n<br />\n今次活動大家努力過 失敗唔緊要 可以不斷檢討改善<br />\n<br />\n但大家未盡力就已經放棄 就係徹底失敗 自我放棄 唔係我哋革命抗爭嘅應有態度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">所以再次呼籲大家<br />\n今晚早啲瞓<br />\n聽朝6點就要開始行動<br />\n各區開花</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後即使失敗 只要你企出嚟盡咗力 之後繼續準時返工做港豬都冇人怪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n香港人！革命！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0f691ea486582d79c4e95d150f89ad19b1d98833","tid":1704233,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee8f0f1fc4ecc6dd2b0caab2a2039df42d36a967","tid":1704233,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:11.000Z","msg":"1111 6am"},{"pid":"447fb07683b5d441da6f8875b5dc6e5ae42b21c6","tid":1704233,"uid":307268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:16.000Z","msg":"雙十一 周圍塞 上晝七點遍地開花 塞佢老母<br />\n阻9交通變相全民罷工 每一個人都要出泥<br />\n<br />\n7AM｛黎明行動｝推到聽朝<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703014\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703014</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雙十一，周圍塞，阻塞交通變相全民罷工 悼念完一定要有行動，手足既血不可白流<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703687\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703687</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」低風險新職業 - 扮工師<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703696\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703696</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n【召集和理非】聽朝7點唔知點做好？入嚟睇下有咩最簡單嘅嘢可以做！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703752</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n聽日可能出現嘅情況<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1703148\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1703148</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n「黎明行動」聽日需要大量無裝備嘅路人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1704043\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1704043</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n驅逐共黨 光復香港"},{"pid":"84367b67df0d652e6faac3d42ba79ab6093cc715","tid":1704233,"uid":240664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:27.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"1731e4ff0692b2a5994dd0a8fb3e60cfe27975b5","tid":1704233,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"香港人 革命"},{"pid":"802076670e2041564bf4cc060bcd577024c1ff0b","tid":1704233,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM9yEVS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM9yEVS.gif&h=36baf129&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9c56e5bef1f081d2305c648b83285777ec321d13","tid":1704233,"uid":150152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:18:33.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"ee52a881d7199828ff05ccfd4e140997013831fe","tid":1704233,"uid":1883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T15:19:07.000Z","msg":"721 831 101"},{"pid":"9820fbbe47616079506b887fa0ee769b54528047","tid":1704233,"uid":77393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"